1980;;Willie & Phil;;American;;Paul Mazursky;;Margot Kidder, Michael Ontkean, Ray Sharkey;;comedy, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Willie_%26_Phil;;The film is set in 1970s New York, amidst the counterculture chic of that era. Willie, a high school English teacher who plays jazz piano, and Phil, a fashion photographer, meet coming out of the Bleecker Street Cinema where Jules et Jim has just been shown and become friends. They both fall in love with Jeannette, a girl from Kentucky.